{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/basic-html/workshop-bookstore-page/step-13","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"workshop-bookstore-page","demoType":null,"title":"Korak 13","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Sada kreiraj drugu knjigu karticu. Dodaj još jedan element za <code>div</code> sa svojstvom <code>class</code> ako ima vrednost <code>card</code>. Pogledaj kako možeš ponovo da koristiš ime klase objekata za više elemenata kako bi koristio dosledan stil.</p>\n</section>","id":"68eca2a795b333ca5fee30a8","hasEditableBoundaries":true,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"basic-html","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/basic-html/workshop-bookstore-page/step-13"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n  <title>XYZ Bookstore Page</title>\n</head>\n\n<body>\n  <h1>XYZ Bookstore</h1>\n  <p>Browse our collection of amazing books!</p>\n  \n  <div class=\"card-container\">\n    <div class=\"card\" id=\"sally-adventure-book\">\n      <h2>Sally's SciFi Adventure</h2>\n      <p>This is an epic story of Sally and her dog Rex as they navigate through other worlds.</p>\n      <button class=\"btn\">Buy Now</button>\n    </div>\n    \n    \n  </div>\n</body>\n\n</html>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[18,20],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da ima dva elementa <code>div</code> sa karakteristikom <code>class</code> sa vrednošću <code>card</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.lengthOf(document.querySelectorAll('.card'), 2);"},{"text":"<p>Drugi element sa klasom <code>card</code> mora biti unutar elementa sa klasom <code>card-container</code>.</p>","test